column4: Anyone else running Ubuntu Netbook Edition?  I swear, I saw "File Manager" (nautalis) in the appications list yesterday -- but can't find it today
if you press alt+f2 and run: nautilus ,does it run?
I have to start from Terminal.  No alt+f2 in UNE :(  But yeah, it runs
ok then run: alacarte ,then add the launcher yourself wherever you wish
